PortGroup           github 1.0

github.setup        facebook rocksdb 5.4.7 rocksdb-

revision            0
categories          databases devel
platforms           darwin
license             BSD

maintainers         stromnov openmaintainer

description         Embedded key-value store for fast storage
long_description    ${description}

homepage            http://rocksdb.org/

checksums           rmd160  386537aa22823f0e541e0ae0207359199356e73a \
                    sha256  7863bd07f04d64260cc4b3d634d54a38e9e542d354ee5388f2532946f97109ce

